com.oracle.bmc.auth

Interface AuthenticationDetailsProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AbstractAuthenticationDetailsProvider, BasicAuthenticationDetailsProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConfigFileAuthenticationDetailsProvider, CustomerAuthenticationDetailsProvider, SimpleAuthenticationDetailsProvider

    public interface AuthenticationDetailsProvider
extends BasicAuthenticationDetailsProvider

    Interface defining a BasicAuthenticationDetailsProvider that also provides the individual components used to create the keyId.

    The BasicAuthenticationDetailsProvider.getKeyId() method should be implemented as “tentantId/userId/fingerprint”. See docs for more information.
